>> source: https://www.eatingonadime.com/homemade-onion-soup-mix/
>> total time: 5 minutes

Mix @dried onion flakes{1/4%cup}, @onion powder{1/4%tsp}, @parsley{1/4%tsp}, @beef bouillon granules{2%Tbsp}, @celery seed{1/8%tsp}, @paprika{1/8%tsp}, and @pepper{1/8%tsp} together is a small mixing bowl. Store in an airtight container until you a ready to use.
